# BlackVideo Mini Player — Development environment overrides
#
# PRODUCTION RELEASE: delete this file entirely.
# The player auto-discovers whisper-cli.exe and the model from build\ at runtime.
#
# DEVELOPMENT: rename this file to .env and fill in paths to override discovery.
# The player loads it from beside the .exe at startup (silent if absent).
#
# ── Whisper ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Path to whisper-cli.exe (from whisper-bin-x64.zip)
BLACKVIDEO_WHISPER_PATH=build\whisper-cli.exe
#
# Path to the GGML model file (swappable — use base/small/medium/large)
BLACKVIDEO_WHISPER_MODEL=build\models\ggml-base.bin

DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=""